  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is a randomized, double-blind, placebo-controlled bilateral study on the effect of
      moisturizing creams on skin barrier function. The hypothesis is that a new active emulsion
      has a better influence on skin barrier function comapred to its placebo.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
